*--------------------------------------------------------------------*
* PARTSPSB.PSB — IMS PSBGEN macro deck fixture (#5057).               *
* Declares a program's PCB view: an IO-PCB (TYPE=TP, message queue)   *
* and a DB-PCB over PARTSDB sensitive to PARTROOT/PARTDETL.           *
* Proves PCB -> SCOPE.Component/ims-pcb (io_pcb flag on the TP PCB,    *
* #5053), DBDNAME -> ACCESSES_TABLE database, SENSEG -> ACCESSES_TABLE *
* segment, PGMNAME -> the serving program.                            *
*--------------------------------------------------------------------*
         PCB   TYPE=TP,EXPRESS=YES
         PCB   TYPE=DB,DBDNAME=PARTSDB,PROCOPT=A,KEYLEN=25,           X
               PCBNAME=PARTPCB
         SENSEG NAME=PARTROOT,PARENT=0
         SENSEG NAME=PARTDETL,PARENT=PARTROOT
         PSBGEN LANG=COBOL,PGMNAME=IMSPART2
         END
